Interface IDVOffEng

    • Method Detail

      • getDeepVioletMajorVersion

        int getDeepVioletMajorVersion()
        Return the Major Version of DeepViolet. Incremented upon significant addition of new features. Existing features could also break code. Callers are urged to test upon implementing new major versions.
        Returns:
        Number indicating DeepVioloet Major Version.

      • getDeepVioletMinorVersion

        int getDeepVioletMinorVersion()
        Return the Minor Version of DeepViolet. Incrememented upon significant improvement to existing features. Callers are urged to test upon implementing new major versions.
        Returns:
        Number indicating DeepVioloet Minor Version.

      • getDeepVioletBuildVersion

        int getDeepVioletBuildVersion()
        Return the Build Version of DeepViolet. Incremented on bug fixes to existing features. It's not anticiapted this any improvemnets will break code. Callers are urged to perform basic unit tests.
        Returns:
        Number indicating DeepVioloet Build Version.

      • getDeepVioletStringVersion

        java.lang.String getDeepVioletStringVersion()
        Return the DeepViolet version string.
        Returns:
        Suitable for printing in log files, displaying in About boxes, etc.

      • getDVOffPrint

        IDVOffPrint getDVOffPrint()
                   throws DVException
        Return offline print engine instance. Useful for reporting featurees that don't require initializing an online host. For example, printing PEM encoded X.509 certificates.
        Returns:
        Offline print engine instance
        Throws:
        DVException - on problems.
